#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_call_to_action
msgid "2,000 parents<br/> brought their kid to our nursery."
msgstr "ຜູ້ປົກຄອງ 2,000 ຄົນ<br/> ໄດ້ພາລູກຫຼານມາທີ່ໂຮງຮຽນລ້ຽງເດັກຂອງພວກເຮົາ."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_banner
msgid "A little place <br/>of paradise"
msgstr "ສະຖານທີ່ນ້ອຍໆ <br/>ແຫ່ງຄວາມສຸກ"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_product_list
msgid "About us"
msgstr "ກ່ຽວກັບພວກເຮົາ"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_image_text
msgid "Activities"
msgstr "ກິດຈະກຳ"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"All activities are planned to meet each child’s individual needs. This "
"approach will help your child to develop to the best of their ability."
msgstr ""
"ທຸກໆກິດຈະກໍາໄດ້ຖືກວາງແຜນໄວ້ເພື່ອຕອບສະໜອງຄວາມຕ້ອງການສ່ວນບຸກຄົນຂອງເດັກແຕ່ລະຄົນ. ວິທີການນີ້ຈະຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ລູ"
"ກຂອງທ່ານພັດທະນາໄດ້ຕາມຄວາມສາມາດສູງສຸດຂອງພວກເຂົາ."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_call_to_action
msgid "Contact us"
msgstr "ຕິດຕໍ່ພວກເຮົາ"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_call_to_action
msgid "Entrust us with your children and go to work with peace of mind"
msgstr "ມອບຄວາມໄວ້ວາງໃຈໃຫ້ພວກເຮົາເບິ່ງແຍງລູກຂອງທ່ານ ແລະ ໄປເຮັດວຽກໄດ້ຢ່າງສະບາຍໃຈ"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_product_list
msgid "Events"
msgstr "ເຫດການ"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_three_columns
msgid "For every kid"
msgstr ""

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_cover
msgid "Kiddo Nursery"
msgstr "ໂຮງຮຽນລ້ຽງເດັກ ຄິດໂດ (Kiddo)"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_picture
msgid "Letting each child explore and grow at their own pace"
msgstr "ປ່ອຍໃຫ້ເດັກແຕ່ລະຄົນໄດ້ສໍາຫຼວດ ແລະ ເຕີບໃຫຍ່ຕາມຈັງຫວະຂອງຕົນເອງ"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_three_columns
msgid "Open-door policy"
msgstr ""

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"Our aim is to make the early years of your child’s life as enjoyable, "
"rewarding and positive as possible."
msgstr ""
"ເປົ້າໝາຍຂອງພວກເຮົາແມ່ນເພື່ອເຮັດໃຫ້ຊ່ວງປີທໍາອິດຂອງຊີວິດລູກຂອງທ່ານ ມີຄວາມມ່ວນຊື່ນ, ມີຄຸນຄ່າ ແລະ ເປັນໄປໃ"
"ນທາງບວກເທົ່າທີ່ຈະເປັນໄປໄດ້."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_three_columns
msgid "Our mission"
msgstr "ພັນທະກິດຂອງພວກເຮົາ"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_picture
msgid ""
"Our qualified staff ensure that each childs' needs are always recognised and"
" fulfilled."
msgstr ""
"ພະນັກງານທີ່ມີຄຸນວຸດທິຂອງພວກເຮົາ ຮັບປະກັນວ່າຄວາມຕ້ອງການຂອງເດັກແຕ່ລະຄົນ ຈະໄດ້ຮັບການຕອບສະໜອງ ແລະ "
"ປະຕິບັດໃຫ້ສໍາເລັດຢູ່ສະເໝີ."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_product_list
msgid "Our team"
msgstr "ທີມງານຂອງພວກເຮົາ"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_image_text
msgid "Our team is composed of experienced nursery nurses."
msgstr "ທີມງານຂອງພວກເຮົາປະກອບດ້ວຍພະຍາບານເດັກທີ່ມີປະສົບການ."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_product_list
msgid "Playground"
msgstr "ສະໜາມເດັກຫຼິ້ນ"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_cover
msgid ""
"The countryside nursery since 2002.<br/>\n"
"        A truly unique service in a highly secure and tranquil setting."
msgstr ""
"ໂຮງຮຽນລ້ຽງເດັກໃນເຂດຊົນນະບົດຕັ້ງແຕ່ປີ 2002.<br/>\n"
"        ບໍລິການທີ່ເປັນເອກະລັກຢ່າງແທ້ຈິງ ໃນສະຖານທີ່ທີ່ມີຄວາມປອດໄພສູງ ແລະ ງຽບສະຫງົບ."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model:ir.model,name:theme_kiddo.model_theme_utils
msgid "Theme Utils"
msgstr "ເຄື່ອງມືຊ່ວຍຈັດການທີມ (Theme Utils)"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_image_text
msgid ""
"They will propose to your children educational activities, playful, varied "
"and adapted to the stage of development."
msgstr ""
"ພວກເຂົາຈະນໍາສະເໜີກິດຈະກໍາການສຶກສາໃຫ້ແກ່ລູກຂອງທ່ານ, ເຊິ່ງມີຄວາມມ່ວນຊື່ນ, ຫຼາກຫຼາຍ ແລະ ເໝາະສົມກັບແຕ່"
"ລະຂັ້ນຕອນຂອງການພັດທະນາ."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_banner
msgid ""
"This is a simple hero unit, a simple jumbotron-style component for calling "
"extra attention to featured content or information."
msgstr ""
"ນີ້ຄືສ່ວນເນັ້ນເນື້ອຫາທີ່ລຽບງ່າຍ, ເປັນອົງປະກອບແບບ jumbotron ເພື່ອສ້າງຄວາມໂດດເດັ່ນໃຫ້ກັບເນື້ອຫາ ຫຼື ຂໍ້ມູນ"
"ທີ່ສໍາຄັນ."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_picture
msgid ""
"Through stimulating and fun activities, our aim<br/>\n"
"        is to promote all areas of a childs' development."
msgstr ""
"ຜ່ານກິດຈະກໍາທີ່ກະຕຸ້ນ ແລະ ມ່ວນຊື່ນ, ເປົ້າໝາຍຂອງພວກເຮົາ<br/>\n"
"        ແມ່ນເພື່ອສົ່ງເສີມທຸກດ້ານຂອງການພັດທະນາເດັກ."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_product_list
msgid "Visit us"
msgstr "ຢ້ຽມຢາມພວກເຮົາ"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"You are welcome to come and see the nursery and meet the team at any time "
"convenient to you."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດເຂົ້າມາຊົມໂຮງຮຽນລ້ຽງເດັກ ແລະ ພົບປະກັບທີມງານໄດ້ທຸກເວລາທີ່ທ່ານສະດວກ."

#. module: theme_kiddo
